different colour deficiencies.

00:18:24.199 --> 00:18:25.400
Important question.

00:18:25.400 --> 00:18:30.900
What should you prioritise in styling?

00:18:30.900 --> 00:18:33.199
Well, above all,

00:18:33.199 --> 00:18:36.300
we are creating products for other people to see.

00:18:36.300 --> 00:18:38.800
So the most important thing

00:18:38.800 --> 00:18:40.199
is that the person on the other side

00:18:40.199 --> 00:18:42.800
is able to understand what is happening

00:18:42.800 --> 00:18:44.599
and extract information.

00:18:44.599 --> 00:18:47.900
So clarity above all,

00:18:47.900 --> 00:18:51.800
